title: BRIEF-TICC Announces Results Of Operations For Quarter Ended Dec 31
text: 15 PM / Updated 7 minutes ago BRIEF-TICC Announces Results Of Operations For Quarter Ended Dec 31 Reuters Staff 1 Min Read Feb 27 (Reuters) - TICC Capital Corp: * TICC ANNOUNCES RESULTS OF OPERATIONS FOR THE QUARTER ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 AND ANNOUNCES QUARTERLY DISTRIBUTION OF $0.20 PER SHARE * TICC CAPITAL CORP - ‍AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2017, NAV PER SHARE WAS $7.55 VERSUS NAV PER SHARE AS OF SEPTEMBER 30, 2017 OF $7.43​ * TICC CAPITAL CORP - ‍FOR QUARTER, RECORDED NET INVESTMENT INCOME OF APPROXIMATELY $7.6 MILLION, OR APPROXIMATELY $0.15 PER SHARE​ * TICC CAPITAL CORP - ‍CORE NET INVESTMENT INCOME FOR QUARTER ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 WAS $9.0 MILLION, OR APPROXIMATELY $0.17 PER SHARE​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
